  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731650/extras/11641a332ae1ecfeedb846aa7fdff8cc.webp?t=1767018204\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731650/extras_big/11641a332ae1ecfeedb846aa7fdff8cc.webp?t=1767018204 width=800 height=27 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create almost infinite numbers of maps with different seeds. One island, several or the Summer Islands mode. From small 100x100 maps up to 1500x1500 maps. From high mountains or just sand islands. Everybody finds his small island in the wide ocean or in the big archipelagos. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731650/extras/9dd49223a6ea440d99988eb73a34fed4.poster.avif?t=1767018204\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731650/extras/9dd49223a6ea440d99988eb73a34fed4.webm?t=1767018204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731650/extras/9dd49223a6ea440d99988eb73a34fed4.mp4?t=1767018204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731650/extras/6b6d7b387de104d8a62df5b0f287e0af.webp?t=1767018204\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731650/extras_big/6b6d7b387de104d8a62df5b0f287e0af.webp?t=1767018204 width=800 height=27 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build cabins, villas or expensive hotels directly on the beach or in the mountains. When a building is finished, tourists can come by boat or plane. The tourists want to be preserved. Build bars, discos, golf courses, supermarkets and many other buildings that are popular with tourists and will make you rich as the owner.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731650/extras/261982926f3308acc638f4ee380f2234.poster.avif?t=1767018204\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731650/extras/261982926f3308acc638f4ee380f2234.webm?t=1767018204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731650/extras/261982926f3308acc638f4ee380f2234.mp4?t=1767018204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731650/extras/cfad583d86a015805f1a81b748f85808.webp?t=1767018204\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731650/extras_big/cfad583d86a015805f1a81b748f85808.webp?t=1767018204 width=800 height=27 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy new buildings from a wide range of building types. From houses and hotels to restaurants, stores, parks attractions etc. Here you can distinguish between mass tourists and luxury tourists. Buildings with luxury tourists earn you more money, but are expensive and have a lower capacity. Also note that mass tourists and luxury tourists have different preferences as to which buildings are nearby. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731650/extras/9b3f93e12eec0c9a387a00ee9df091ee.poster.avif?t=1767018204\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731650/extras/9b3f93e12eec0c9a387a00ee9df091ee.webm?t=1767018204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731650/extras/9b3f93e12eec0c9a387a00ee9df091ee.mp4?t=1767018204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731650/extras/3d3c47a422352bb7c7489282251850a1.webp?t=1767018204\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731650/extras_big/3d3c47a422352bb7c7489282251850a1.webp?t=1767018204 width=800 height=27 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Borrow money or pay off your debts. Go out and advertise, or take out insurance. Check if your buildings are doing well and you can raise the rent. Hire consultants to protect you from sabotage, for example. Or would you rather unlock more sabotage? That is entirely up to you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731650/extras/d00255e9a0b3cafef9ffb9ef5a8095a1.poster.avif?t=1767018204\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731650/extras/d00255e9a0b3cafef9ffb9ef5a8095a1.webm?t=1767018204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731650/extras/d00255e9a0b3cafef9ffb9ef5a8095a1.mp4?t=1767018204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731650/extras/eefdfec2c0142875a661a6ba848cfe89.webp?t=1767018204\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731650/extras_big/eefdfec2c0142875a661a6ba848cfe89.webp?t=1767018204 width=800 height=27 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unfortunately there are also natural disasters that can destroy your buildings. Whether tornado, earthquake or meteorite, everything is possible.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In quiet times the competition comes from your enemy and expands over your land. Maybe there are some sabotage possibilities! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731650/extras/67db00029bc078ae626d056e6dd0dad1.poster.avif?t=1767018204\" width=616 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731650/extras/67db00029bc078ae626d056e6dd0dad1.webm?t=1767018204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731650/extras/67db00029bc078ae626d056e6dd0dad1.mp4?t=1767018204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731650/extras/598e16ecb745efa6e6cecd6eb644acba.webp?t=1767018204\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731650/extras_big/598e16ecb745efa6e6cecd6eb644acba.webp?t=1767018204 width=800 height=27 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the Map Editor you can not only create your perfect map. You can also fill it with events. Which buildings should be unlocked under which conditions. A match where you cannot build roads or there is no minimap? You want natural disasters to occur under certain conditions at a certain place? Try it out! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731650/extras/954f4322f493d9a74ba3bf502c33ccc0.poster.avif?t=1767018204\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731650/extras/954f4322f493d9a74ba3bf502c33ccc0.webm?t=1767018204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731650/extras/954f4322f493d9a74ba3bf502c33ccc0.mp4?t=1767018204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731650/extras/11641a332ae1ecfeedb846aa7fdff8cc.webp?t=1767018204\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731650/extras_big/11641a332ae1ecfeedb846aa7fdff8cc.webp?t=1767018204 width=800 height=27 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create almost infinite numbers of maps with different seeds. One island, several or the Summer Islands mode. From small 100x100 maps up to 1500x1500 maps. From high mountains or just sand islands. Everybody finds his small island in the wide ocean or in the big archipelagos. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731650/extras/9dd49223a6ea440d99988eb73a34fed4.poster.avif?t=1767018204\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731650/extras/9dd49223a6ea440d99988eb73a34fed4.webm?t=1767018204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731650/extras/9dd49223a6ea440d99988eb73a34fed4.mp4?t=1767018204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731650/extras/6b6d7b387de104d8a62df5b0f287e0af.webp?t=1767018204\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731650/extras_big/6b6d7b387de104d8a62df5b0f287e0af.webp?t=1767018204 width=800 height=27 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build cabins, villas or expensive hotels directly on the beach or in the mountains. When a building is finished, tourists can come by boat or plane. The tourists want to be p